  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature Casts a Spell with the mental trait.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You have at least 1 Focus Point.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>When a foe Casts a Spell that has the mental trait and you can see or otherwise detect its manifestations, you can use your psychic powers to disrupt it. You expend 1 Focus Point to counter the triggering creature's casting of the spell. You then attempt to counteract the triggering spell using your spellcasting counteract modifier.</p>"
